{"tid":1452520,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"給沒有企過出來的人","createTime":"2019-08-12T01:34:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T01:35:15.000Z","uid":54250,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"03b20787beae070c933b4915579d562a06559343","tid":1452520,"uid":54250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:34:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OzoB80w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOzoB80w.jpg&h=e55a24bd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6RKE6Nc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6RKE6Nc.jpg&h=a44b1201&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">他朝你或你的子女君體也相同啊</span></span><br />\n<br />\n去唔去到都廣傳<br />\n<br />\n一人一 狂洗連登post [時事台]<br />\n唔該你出一份力，肯出post，聽日就係人都知入機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 標題：「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大群：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=hP6DzN64O1sWLJLr9GARkaCH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=0d3d92c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=hP6DzN64O1sWLJLr9GARkaCH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=d6067f8c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>"},{"pid":"444d62d6bdb15ad620eb7f817017ee51b0781eeb","tid":1452520,"uid":291619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:35:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}